ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Madagascar -- Convention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the CONVENTION between the Government of Canada and Government of the REPUBLIC OF MADAGASCAR for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME.
